When requesting a refund, please provide the following information:

a. Your name and email address associated with your account; b. The date of purchase and the amount paid; c. The reason for the refund request; and d. Any other relevant information or documentation that supports your request.

We will review your refund request and respond within a reasonable time frame. If your request is approved, we will process the refund using the original payment method. Please note that the time it takes for the refund to appear in your account may vary depending on your bank or payment provider.

Refund Limitations

